bandsintown_response.description:
The Wyatt Act officially endorses Breakfast for Chancellor. www.thewyattact.com

The SMASH Arcade presents an evening dedicated to Electoral Catharsis - for your personal mental health and well-being and in a completely NON-hyperbolic, exaggerated statement… for the collective well-being of AMERICA! 

$10 at the door gets you into the arcade with tickets in hand. How, what and the amount you smash is up to YOU! That’s freedom, baby!

Ticket URL
https://electoral-catharsis.eventbrite.com/

What’s that? You want to .:SMASH A CAR:. to bits and pieces? We’ve got it on lockdown! 

.:THROWING GALLERY:. Test your pitching arm! 

.:DROP ZONE:. Get real high (but not in a prop 64 kinda way) and smash things with gravity assist!

.:RALLY BOWL:. Our good friends are hosting, all smash oriented lanes! (https://www.facebook.com/RallyBowl/) 

Plus 
.:Election Results on the BIG screen:. 
.:Live Music by Protected Left and The Wyatt Act!:.
.:Food & Drinks:. 
and more surprises!

Be sure to click that you’re going. Not only does it help us prepare for a SMASHING good time (see what we did there?) We’ll update y'all with more details on parking, performers, and other extras soon.

Location: NIMBY is Oakland's premier DIY space. 5 minute bike ride from Colesium Bart along a protected pedestrian & bike path or 10 minute drive from the bridge. 


*!CLOSED TOE SHOES REQUIRED!*
***This event is non-partisan and does not advocate violence towards people, just inanimate objects, especially those that are most gratifying to smash.***

^^ Ages 18 and up. ^^

https://www.facebook.com/events/193984354371695/
